data.description: Hey there! I've got something exciting to share with you today. If you're on the lookout for a cozy home in the ANTIETAM school district area, then this one might just tick all your boxes. Let me take you on a virtual tour of this fantastic 3-bedroom gem that comes with its very own parking space. As soon as you step inside, you'll be greeted by an inviting atmosphere with plenty of natural light flowing through the windows, making the whole place feel warm and open. The spacious bedrooms offer ample room for relaxation and personalization, while the communal spaces provide a perfect hub for entertaining friends and family. And let's not forget about the convenient parking, ensuring that you never have to stress about finding a spot again. Come on over and discover everything this lovely home has to offer!  Great Heating Furnace, Great Central A/C and Good Water heater all property mechanic are in good shape.
